sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / SDK
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as Trainer Controller<br/>(opendatahub namespace)
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pods<br/>(user namespace)
    participant PeerPod as Peer Training Pods

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        note over User,TrainingPod: Flow 1: TrainJob Reconciliation (PyTorch Distributed)

        User->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / kubeconfig
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-...-trainjob<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS (self-signed)<br/>Auth: AdmissionReview
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Allowed / Denied
        K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob created

        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: TrainJob<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create JobSet CR<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PodGroup CR<br/>(if co-scheduling enabled)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>(RHOAI: per-TrainJob isolation)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+

        K8sAPI->>JobSetCtrl: Watch event: JobSet
        JobSetCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Training Pods
        K8sAPI-->>TrainingPod: Pods scheduled

        TrainingPod->>PeerPod: NCCL/gRPC rendezvous<br/>TCP/29500 plaintext<br/>NetworkPolicy: same-job pods only
        PeerPod-->>TrainingPod: Distributed training communication
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        note over Controller,TrainingPod: Flow 2: Progression Tracking (RHOAI-specific)

        Controller->>K8sAPI: List pods (APIReader direct etcd read)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod IPs for TrainJob

        loop Poll interval (5s-300s configurable)
            Controller->>TrainingPod: GET /metrics (rank-0 pod)<br/>HTTP/28080 plaintext<br/>Auth: None (NetworkPolicy-secured)
            TrainingPod-->>Controller: Training metrics JSON<br/>(sanitized: NaN/Infinity handled)
        end

        Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH TrainJob annotation<br/>(progress data)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        note over Controller,PeerPod: Flow 3: MPI Training Job

        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create SSH Secret<br/>(ECDSA P-521 key pair, immutable)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create hostfile ConfigMap<br/>(node endpoints + slot counts)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create JobSet CR<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+

        K8sAPI->>JobSetCtrl: Watch event: JobSet
        JobSetCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create MPI Pods

        TrainingPod->>PeerPod: SSH (MPI launcher → workers)<br/>TCP/22<br/>ECDSA P-521 key exchange<br/>Auth: SSH key pair from Secret
    end
